{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>DEMO DURATION: 10 minutes</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Heart of Artemisa</strong> is a <strong>rhythm adventure game</strong>, with <strong>dungeon crawler &amp; Roguelite elements</strong>, where the player has to defeat enemies and solve puzzles <strong>at the beat of music</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game\u2019s aesthetic has a <strong>retro 16-bit pixel art</strong> style and a mix of dancing and <strong>spooky music</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226410/extras/artemisa_03.gif?t=1732574087\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players will explore a <strong>2D top down view world</strong> with caves and dark dungeons of the deep depths of a mysterious and cursed dungeon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Movement and combat system are based on following the rhythm of the music</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This feature won\u2019t be strict or obligatory. Players can proceed through the game without following the beat of music, but following the beat will make their adventure easier since the attacks will cause more damage to enemies. The more hits you do at the beat, more damage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226410/extras/Screenshot_HoArtemisa04.png?t=1732574087\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226410/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732574087","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226410/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1732574087","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226410/6724caab3205457d494e5c49183aa41990524799/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732574087","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/